name: Generosity
description:
Sometimes we give up time, work, things, or money to improve the lives of others, and that is very good. Other times we share relationships so that everyone involved benefits, and that's fine too. However, for me, the most necessary kind of generosity is expressed in the judgments we make of others. It bears great benefits for everyone involved, and we pay little attention to it.

* 𝗧𝗢𝗔 (𝗧𝗼𝗸𝗲𝗻 𝗼𝗳 𝗮𝗽𝗽𝗿𝗲𝗰𝗶𝗮𝘁𝗶𝗼𝗻)
